---
/**
 * Architecture Overview
 * Static structural explanation of monitoring pipeline.
 */
---

<section class="py-20 border-t border-outline/50 bg-surface">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl text-center">

    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-12 text-content">
      Monitoring Architecture
    </h2>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-8 text-sm md:text-base text-content-light">

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="font-medium text-content mb-2">Browser</div>
        <div>Telemetry Script</div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-content-light">→</div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="font-medium text-content mb-2">API</div>
        <div>api.protowebstudio.com</div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-content-light">→</div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="font-medium text-content mb-2">Risk Engine</div>
        <div>Deterministic Scoring</div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-content-light">→</div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="font-medium text-content mb-2">Dashboard</div>
        <div>Operational Control Layer</div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 text-sm text-content-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      All events are token-authenticated, timestamp-validated,
      and idempotently processed before risk evaluation.
    </div>

  </div>
</section>